data.name: PoolsizeBox.ToolTip
data.value:
Allocates graphics memory to texture streaming. Value should be lower than GPU memory size. 2GB is recommended for the HD Texture Pack.
"Infinite" = Streaming limit will be removed. Useful for in-game texture dumping and debugging, but may cause crashes.

data.name: texpacksupportbox.ToolTip
data.value:
Disabled - Vanilla texture settings.
Asylum Reborn - 4K character textures and support for Asylum Reborn Texture Pack.
Ultra HD - 4K texture support for every texture group. Requires AsylumHD by FCH823 (or equivalent) to be installed or will result in crashes. Compatible with Asylum Reborn Texture Pack.
Custom - Assign values for texture groups individually. Intended for advanced users and any subsequent texture packs requiring different values.
